headline: Where Will Costco Stock Be in 1 Year?
summary: Costco Wholesale's (NASDAQ: COST) stock has earned considerable returns for its investors in recent years.  The stock marched steadily higher in 2023 and 2024 but has endured a pullback amid the sell-off in the broad market and is now near correction territory.  Indeed, Costco has evolved into one of the world's most successful retailers, and its rising stock price likely reflects its strong position in the marketplace.
